description: Skyler is a 22 year old from Florida who is in his junior year of college to become an accountant.He is into taking care of his body and is very athletic.His favorite thing to do is to be outside surfing or babe watching on the sands. Skyler says he is currently single and slightly looking, but isn't ready to commit his entire life to someone. We have a feeling it won't be long before a young lady will be all over him...and how could you blame her?So sit back and enjoy the beautiful Skyler as he kicks it on the couch, rinses off in the shower, and strokes himself to completion while lying on the bed.Enjoy!
title: Skyler
